channel.title: Download Complete PSP Saved Files
channel.description:
Go to www.PSP-Saves.net and join.(This is not an advertisement)
Go to downloads>search for the game you want done
Download the saved game.
Plug your usb to your psp to your computer, or put your memory stick in the mem stick reader( if you have one).
Go to the drive your psp is and go to PSP>Save data
Copy the file you downloaded, it should me named something like [code]ULUS10036001[/code](do not rename it!!!) Thats only an example, do not rename the file you downloaded!
Paste it in PSP>SAVEDATA
Put it in your psp and heeeey 100% complete game =]
Games I have gotten: Need for speed most wanted 5-1-0 Grand theft auto liberty city stories Grand theft auto vice city stories Need for speed rivals
enjoy.
